OL,3,C'Rehash of dangerous system': Fears of
OL,4,COfsted's proposed grading scale
OL,6,FThe sister of headteacher Ruth Perry,
OL,7,Fwho took her own life after an Ofsted
OL,8,Finspection at her school, fears the
OL,9,Fwatchdog's new grading reports are a
OL,10,F"rehash" of the "dangerous" system.
OL,12,FThe government announced last year
OL,13,Fthat headline Ofsted grades for
OL,14,Foverall effectiveness for schools in
OL,15,FEngland would be scrapped.
OL,17,FPreviously, Ofsted awarded one of four
OL,18,Fsingle-phrase inspection judgments:
OL,19,Foutstanding, good, requires
OL,20,Fimprovement and inadequate.
