OL,3,C'Rehash of dangerous system': Fears of
OL,4,COfsted's proposed grading scale
OL,6,FThe reforms follow criticism of the
OL,7,Finspection system following the death
OL,8,Fof headteacher Mrs Perry, who took her
OL,9,Fown life in 2023 after an Ofsted
OL,10,Freport downgraded her Caversham
OL,11,FPrimary School in Reading from the
OL,12,Fhighest to the lowest overall
OL,13,Feffectiveness rating over safeguarding
OL,14,Fconcerns.
