OL,3,C'Rehash of dangerous system': Fears of
OL,4,COfsted's proposed grading scale
OL,6,F"It is two years since Ruth's death,
OL,7,Fand a year since Sir Martyn Oliver
OL,8,Ftook charge of Ofsted.
OL,10,F"Ofsted says it has listened, but it
OL,11,Fstill does not appear to have
OL,12,Fadequately learned.
OL,14,F"I am worried that this proposal is a
OL,15,Frehash of the discredited and
OL,16,Fdangerous system it is meant to
OL,17,Freplace."
