OL,3,C'Rehash of dangerous system': Fears of
OL,4,COfsted's proposed grading scale
OL,6,FProfessor Waters added that the
OL,7,Fproposal appears to have fed the
OL,8,Fsingle-word judgments "through an
OL,9,Fonline thesaurus", adding that "other
OL,10,Felements of the report card design are
OL,11,Fill-thought-through and potentially
OL,12,Fdangerous".
OL,14,FWhat is Ofsted's new grading system,
OL,15,Fand how will schools be assessed?
OL,17,FSchools in England could now be graded
OL,18,Facross a variety of different areas `
OL,19,Fincluding attendance and inclusion `
OL,20,Fusing a colour-coded five-point scale.
