OL,3,C'Rehash of dangerous system': Fears of
OL,4,COfsted's proposed grading scale
OL,6,FUnder Ofsted's proposed new report
OL,7,Fcard system, schools would be rated
OL,8,Fusing colour-coded categories, from
OL,9,Fred for "causing concern" and orange
OL,10,Ffor "attention needed" to shades of
OL,11,Fgreen for "secure," "strong," and
OL,12,F"exemplary."
OL,14,FUnder the inspectorate's proposals,
OL,15,Fschools could be assessed in at least
OL,16,Feight areas, each graded and
OL,17,Fsummarised in a report card for
OL,18,Fparents.
