OL,3,C'Rehash of dangerous system': Fears of
OL,4,COfsted's proposed grading scale
OL,6,FInspectors will also look at how well
OL,7,Fschools support vulnerable and
OL,8,Fdisadvantaged children, including
OL,9,Fthose with special educational needs
OL,10,Fand disabilities (Send), as part of a
OL,11,Fnew focus on inclusion.
OL,13,FOfsted is also proposing that all
OL,14,Fschools with an identified need for
OL,15,Fimprovement will receive monitoring
OL,16,Fcalls and visits to check that timely
OL,17,Faction is being taken to raise
OL,18,Fstandards.
