OL,6,FThis includes schools with any
OL,7,Fevaluation area graded "attention
OL,8,Fneeded".
OL,10,FFrom November, it is also proposed
OL,11,Fthat Ofsted will no longer carry out
OL,12,Fungraded inspections of state schools
OL,13,Fwhich means every school will know
OL,14,Fthat its next routine Ofsted
OL,15,Finspection will be a full, graded one.
