OL,6,FThe proposals have been criticised by
OL,7,FPaul Whiteman, general secretary of
OL,8,Fschool leaders' union NAHT, who said
OL,9,Fthey "suggest an inspectorate
OL,10,Fdetermined to hold on to a model of
OL,11,Finspection that is long past its sell-
OL,12,Fby date".
OL,14,FPepe Di'Iasio, general secretary of
OL,15,Fthe Association of School and College
OL,16,FLeaders (ASCL), also said the proposed
OL,17,Fschool report cards "appear to be even
OL,18,Fworse than the single-word judgments
OL,19,Fthey replace".
