OL,6,FPreviously, schools were judged on the
OL,7,Fquality of education, behaviour and
OL,8,Fattitudes, personal development and
OL,9,Fleadership and management.
OL,11,FIn the consultation document, Ofsted
OL,12,Fsaid: "We will continue to call out
OL,13,Funacceptable practice, as we have
OL,14,Falways done. That is our duty, and
OL,15,Fit's a moral duty as much as a
