OL,3,C'Rehash of dangerous system': Fears of
OL,4,COfsted's proposed grading scale
OL,6,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,7,Fwill make a speech about the overhaul,
OL,8,Fas a 12-week consultation is launched
OL,9,Fon Monday.
OL,11,FPhillipson will cast the reforms as a
OL,12,F"more rigorous system, raising the bar
OL,13,Fof our expectations, on what good
OL,14,Freally looks like when it comes to the
OL,15,Ffutures of our children".
OL,17,FHer wide-ranging speech is also
OL,18,Fexpected to set out the Government's
OL,19,Feducation plans, including delivering
OL,20,Fimproved outcomes for children from
OL,21,Fdisadvantaged backgrounds.
